<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 01:00:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>通胀数据温和后美元下跌；新西兰联储决定前新西兰坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-after-benign-inflation-data-kiwi-firm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-08-14/</link><description>美元兑主要货币隔夜暴跌后，周三仍处于不利地位，因美国生产者价格的良好数据增强了对美联储今年降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-after-benign-inflation-data-kiwi-firm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔加拉法、山东队晋级亚冠联赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-gharafa-shandong-secure-berths-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-14/</link><description>卡塔尔的阿尔加拉法队和中国的山东泰山队在周五的新亚冠联赛小组赛抽签中占据了剩下的两个席位，周二的附加赛分别战胜了沙巴布·阿赫利队和曼谷联队。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-gharafa-shandong-secure-berths-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>加州允许中国机器人出租车公司文远知行进行乘客测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/california-allows-chinese-robotaxi-firm-weride-test-with-passengers-2024-08-13/</link><description>根据加州公用事业监管机构的许可，中国自动驾驶初创公司文远知行已获得加州批准，可以测试其无人驾驶汽车载客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/california-allows-chinese-robotaxi-firm-weride-test-with-passengers-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示日本8月份商业信心因中国经济放缓而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-aug-slips-chinas-slowdown-2024-08-13/</link><description>路透短观月度调查周三发现，日本制造商对 8 月份商业状况的信心略有下降，服务业情绪有所缓和，原因是中国需求低迷打压了企业信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-aug-slips-chinas-slowdown-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：市场摆脱了波动，但这种情况会持续吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-13/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国陆军情报分析师承认向中国出售军事机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-army-intelligence-analyst-pleads-guilty-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-08-13/</link><description>美国司法部表示，一名美国陆军情报分析员周二承认密谋向中国出售军事机密的指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 21:17:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-army-intelligence-analyst-pleads-guilty-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月新增贷款创15年来新低 预计将出台更多政策措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-new-loans-hit-15-year-low-july-more-policy-steps-expected-2024-08-13/</link><description>受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，7月份中国银行贷款降幅超预期，创近15年来最低，并引发人们对央行可能推出更多宽松举措的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 18:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-new-loans-hit-15-year-low-july-more-policy-steps-expected-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>同方威视在欧盟调查中否认接受中国国家补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/nuctech-denies-receiving-chinese-state-subsidies-eu-probe-2024-08-13/</link><description>中国安全公司同方威视周二重申，在欧盟普通法院周一驳回其要求欧盟委员会暂时中止检查该公司决定的请求后，该公司并未获得中国国家补贴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/nuctech-denies-receiving-chinese-state-subsidies-eu-probe-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，华为准备推出新的人工智能芯片，在中国挑战英伟达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-readies-new-ai-chip-challenge-nvidia-china-wsj-reports-2024-08-13/</link><description>《华尔街日报》周二援引消息人士的话报道称，在美国制裁之际，中国华为技术有限公司即将推出一款用于人工智能的新芯片，以在中国挑战英伟达。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-readies-new-ai-chip-challenge-nvidia-china-wsj-reports-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>基里巴斯大选与中国关系密切，气候立场面临考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kiribati-goes-election-which-china-ties-climate-stance-face-test-2024-08-13/</link><description>偏远的太平洋岛国基里巴斯将于周三举行全国选举，选民面临的主要问题是政府与中国的密切关系以及在全球气候倡导上采取更温和的立场，以应对生活成本压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kiribati-goes-election-which-china-ties-climate-stance-face-test-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国对外投资配额紧缩促使外国资产管理公司发挥创造力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-outbound-investing-quota-crunch-spurs-foreign-asset-managers-get-creative-2024-08-13/</link><description>尽管美国和日本市场近期遭遇抛售，但中国投资者对境外投资的需求不断飙升，导致外资银行和基金管理公司争先恐后地分配境外投资配额。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 07:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-outbound-investing-quota-crunch-spurs-foreign-asset-managers-get-creative-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>美银调查显示，8 月份投资者减少了股票配置，转向现金配置</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/investors-reduced-allocations-stocks-moved-cash-august-bofa-survey-shows-2024-08-13/</link><description>美国银行周二公布的基金经理调查显示，随着全球经济增长预期降至八个月来的最低水平，投资者在 8 月份增加了现金配置，并减少了股票的超配仓位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 07:44:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/investors-reduced-allocations-stocks-moved-cash-august-bofa-survey-shows-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>什么是人民币套利交易？它与日元有何不同？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/what-is-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-how-is-it-different-yens-2024-08-13/</link><description>日元资助的套利交易平仓引发的全球市场抛售让人民币成为人们关注的焦点，人民币也被广泛用作廉价融资货币。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/what-is-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-how-is-it-different-yens-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺再提供数十亿资金援助受灾农区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-financial-support-restore-agricultural-output-after-floods-2024-08-13/</link><description>中国央行周二表示，在最近的极端天气导致约 600 万英亩农作物受损后，将向银行额外提供 1000 亿元人民币（140 亿美元），以支持受洪水破坏的地区的重建。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-financial-support-restore-agricultural-output-after-floods-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称与中国就南海前哨基地达成的协议有待未来审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-air-force-actions-scarborough-shoal-coercive-aggressive-2024-08-13/</link><description>菲律宾周二表示，与中国达成的一项避免在争议浅滩向部队补给任务期间发生对抗的安排可能会受到未来的审查，而几天前，两国在南中国海其他地方最近爆发了冲突。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-air-force-actions-scarborough-shoal-coercive-aggressive-2024-08-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>